# Quotation Generate Workflow

## Overview

Convert verified proposal templates (.md) into professional PowerPoint presentations and PDF documents with viAct branding.

## Workflow: 4 Steps

```
Step 1: Create Output Directory
  → ./output/[Project]_[YYYYMMDD]_[HHMMSS]/
  → Create slides/ subdirectory

Step 2: Generate HTML Slides
  → Parse template.md (12 sections)
  → Use SLIDE_TEMPLATES.md (7 templates)
  → Apply viAct branding (#00AEEF blue, white text)
  → Prevent text overflow (margins: 0 120pt 85pt 40pt)
  → Generate architecture diagram if needed

Step 3: Generate PowerPoint
  → Use pptx skill (html2pptx workflow)
  → Output: [Project]_proposal.pptx

Step 4: Generate PDF
  → Use pdf skill (PPTX → PDF)
  → Output: [Project]_proposal.pdf
```

## Input Requirements

- **Template file**: Verified proposal template (`.md` format)
- **No placeholders**: Template must NOT contain `[PLACEHOLDER_ID]` tags
- **12 sections**: Must follow standard viAct proposal structure
- **Dependencies**: pptx skill, pdf skill must be available

## Output Structure

```
./output/
└── [ProjectName]_[YYYYMMDD]_[HHMMSS]/
    ├── [Project]_proposal.pptx
    ├── [Project]_proposal.pdf
    └── slides/                      (optional: HTML source)
        ├── slide01_cover.html
        ├── slide02_requirements.html
        └── ...
```

